	   <tr><td colspan=2>WOOT Tigerpaw!!<br>This is the bottomline. Mobs hate bards. But there is some rationale to it. Aggro is based on not only how much damage you do, but on how much more difficult you make it for the MOB to kill its target. Same reason that when a cleric heals&nbsp;&nbsp;he gets smacked. So if you take into account your melee damage, extra damage group is doing because of various buffs or damage mob isnt doing for the same reason, and if you do any kind of snaring/debuff on it, you can see why we bards are always on top of the hate list. As for wandering aggros, I honesly don't have a goos answer. I notice all kinds of crazy faction hits, sometimes as i enter the zone. I would assume it is a result of the underlying faction/hate motivation that all mobs have. Of course it could be that they all hate us cocky bards.<br><br>Wilderae (Twilight Requiem)<br>41 rockstar<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
