	   <tr><td colspan=2>i have&nbsp;&nbsp;found the info  in question in the eq manual  supplemental  and  tried it does work  just not very  well setting the delay   is the   tricky  part  but you can  twist 3  songs  with 1 hot key  so it is cool  here is how it works  <br><br>/pause 20   (  pause  before cast or gesture  in milliseconds upto 600 )<br>/cast 1      (  cast  the spell gem 1 -8  )<br><br>expamle <br>/sit off<br>/pause 20 ,/cast 1 <br>/pause 30 ,/cast 2 <br>/pause 20 ,/cast 3<br>/sit on <br><br>the  catch is  this   the ( pause )  even  though it is stated first  happens  after the  cast .<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
